text:
I brought some pudding.
Would you like one, Producer-san?

Oh, the pudding Amana was enjoying earlier
was handmade by Chiyuki...

Yeah, it's delicious.
The custard flavor is rich, and the caramel is fragrant...

When you're tired,
sweet treats and rice taste delicious, don't they?
Hehe, I'm glad it suits your taste, Producer-san.

Oh, sorry Chiyuki.
I didn't mean to imply anything...

...I'm happy, you know.
Knowing that you made it for Amana.

It's just...
I feel hesitant to say "I'm here for you"...
But, I just want you to feel a little better...

Since it's our unit live, I don't want you to
regret feeling like you didn't give it your all...

...Just knowing that there's someone who cares
enough to worry about you can be encouraging.
